{"lastModified":1774013970038,"uri":"c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"This elegant 68-foot Ferretti is based in Mykonos and offers a comfortable and enjoyable way to explore the Greek islands.\n Recently refitted in 2026, the yacht features refreshed interiors and modern upgrades that make every trip relaxing and easy for guests. \nAll cabins have been newly re-upholstered and iclude electric shades for extra comfort and privacy. The salon is bright and welcoming, also fitted with electric shades.The outdoor areas are spacious and perfect for relaxing, enjoying the sea breeze, and taking in the beautiful views.\nAt night, the underwater lights create a special atmosphere while the yacht is at anchor. \n\nThe yacht is equipped with new generators, a brand new jet ski, and a variety of water toys for guests who want to enjoy the sea and have fun on the water. On board, guests are taken careof by a very experienced captain with more than 15 years on this specific yacht, along with a certified chef who prepares fresh meals during the trip.\n\nThe yacht is available for daily and multi-day charters.","blueprint":{"name":"SIMPLY BRILLIANT","images":["/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::dca283b0-17ba-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::dca2d1d0-17ba-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::dca17240-17ba-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::dcaa4be0-17ba-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::dca1e770-17ba-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1