bel":"Cooker/Stove"},{"label":"Oven"},{"label":"Coffee Machine"},{"label":"Microwave "},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Dishwasher"},{"label":"Washing Machine"},{"label":"Heating System"},{"label":"Outside Shower"},{"label":"Sun Pads"},{"label":"GPS Plotter"},{"label":"Solar Panels"},{"label":"Teak deck (whole deck, not only the cockpit)"},{"label":"Electric winches"},{"label":"Radar"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Autopilot"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Bow thruster"},{"label":"Bathing platform"},{"label":"Generator"}],"toys":[{"label":"Jetski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"E-foil","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"6"},{"label":"SUP","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wakeboard","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Tubes","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Swimming Platform","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water toys","quantity":"1"}],"entertainment":["Wi-Fi","Outside deck speakers","Radio CD / MP3 player / Audio system","Inside speakers","Flat screen TV"]},"crew":[{"name":"Panos Zikos","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::acd8e800-2461-11f1-a13b-87b4b751776d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Panos, born and raised in Athens, developed a deep connection with boats and the sea from a young age. \nWith over 15 years of experience at sea, he brings deep knowledge, professionalism, and genuine passion to every journey. Coming from a family with a rich seafaring tradition, he spent his childhood and summer holidays sailing and exploring coastal destinations. This lifelong relationship with the sea has shaped not only his skills and experience, but also his strong love for sailing and hospitality.\nHis extensive experience allows him to operate with confidence, safety, and attention to detail. \nWith his deep knowledge of the destinations visited, Captain Panos offers guests unique insights, smooth navigation, and carefully selected routes that highlight the beauty of each location. \nA true water toys enthusiast, Panos is highly experienced in handling and guiding guests through a wide range of water activities, ensuring both fun and safety while on board.\n“Simply Brilliant” will operate a very busy schedule with the highest expectations. \nCaptain Panos and his crew have all the skills to meet or exceed these expectations."},{"name":"Nikos Minadakis","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::fe0368e0-2461-11f1-a13b-87b4b751776d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nikos is a highly motivated and dedicated steward, known for his professionalism, strong work ethic, and positive energy on board. His proactive attitude and team-oriented mindset make him a reliable and valued member of the crew, contributing to the smooth and efficient operation of every charter. In addition to his steward responsibilities, Nikos is a certified chef, bringing valuable culinary expertise to the onboard experience. His passion for cooking, combined with his training and natural talent, results in consistently high-quality meals that are frequently praised by guests and considered a highlight of their journey.\nOriginally from Crete, an island rich in history and renowned for its delicious cuisine, Nikos has countless stories and insights to share with guests on board. Holding a speedboat license, he is also an experienced and confident operator of watercraft. \nHe is especially kind and attentive with children, ensuring they feel safe and engaged throughout the voyage. With a genuine love for the sea, excellent communication skills, and great attention to detail, Nikos plays an essential role in delivering a refined and memorable yachting experience.."},{"name":"Roni Sander","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::1e5dddb0-1d97-11ef-8d0a-77dae4f04fdd::assets::234a8fc0-2462-11f1-a13b-87b4b751776d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Roni is a reliable and proactive deckhand, respected for his hands-on approach, strong sense of responsibility, and commitment to excellence. With comprehensive knowledge of yacht operations, he ensures that the vessel’s exterior is impeccably maintained at all times. \nHis expertise spans line handling, assisting with docking and anchoring, and managing tenders and watersports activities. Roni takes pride in every aspect of yacht upkeep and is always ready to support both crew and guests wherever needed.\nKnown for his friendly and approachable nature, he effortlessly builds rapport with guests and colleagues alike, enhancing the welcoming and professional atmosphere on board. \nRoni’s dedication to smooth day-to-day operations ensures a seamless, safe, and enjoyable yachting experience for everyone."}],"pricing":{"dayPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":455000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":455000,"unit":"DAY"},"dayPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":505000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":505000,"unit":"DAY"},"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":710000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":710000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2555000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2555000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season (April - May - September - October): Full Day Charter","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-11-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":455000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"DAY","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":455000,"amount":455000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.24}}],"total":455000,"subTotal":